{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_1m7mj1dqt9ky4o4f18odwh","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"432429622","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/claude-code/2026-07-21T17-57-52-415Z/tokenwarden-docs-from-code-1/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","content":"# Cache API\n\nThis module provides a simple in-memory cache implementation using a `Map` under the hood.\n\n## createCache()\n\nCreates and returns a new cache instance with basic CRUD operations.\n\n```javascript\nimport { createCache } from './cache'\n\nconst cache = createCache()\n```\n\nReturns an object with the following methods:\n\n## Methods\n\n### get(key)\n\nRetrieves a value from the cache by key.\n\n- **Parameters:**\n  - `key` - The cache key to look up\n- **Returns:** The cached value, or `undefined` if not found\n\n```javascript\nconst value = cache.get('my-key')\n```\n\n### set(key, value)\n\nStores a value in the cache.\n\n- **Parameters:**\n  - `key` - The cache key\n  - `value` - The value to cache\n- **Returns:** The cached value\n\n```javascript\ncache.set('my-key', 'my-value')\n```\n\n### delete(key)\n\nRemoves a value from the cache by key.\n\n- **Parameters:**\n  - `key` - The cache key to delete\n- **Returns:** `true` if the key existed and was deleted, `false` otherwise\n\n```javascript\nconst wasDeleted = cache.delete('my-key')\n```\n\n### clear()\n\nRemoves all entries from the cache.\n\n```javascript\ncache.clear()\n```\n\n---\n\n**Source:** `bench-targets/docs/src/cache.mjs`\n"}}],"model":"qwen/qwen3.5-9b","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":5445,"output_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":5337},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1ab3c781-cce9-4575-add2-00752e1855f7","uuid":"41ccc521-1b66-4a03-a658-6b983b020a8c","timestamp":"2026-07-21T20:48:25.051Z"}
